videos.description: David Blough takes the keeper to score the 5-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Blough keeps it himself to give Purdue early lead

videos.description: Tario Fuller runs untouched 36 yards to extend the Boilermakers lead.
videos.headline: Fuller escapes the defense for six

videos.description: Richie Worship bullies his way into the end zone as the Boilermakers pour it on in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Worship pounds it in for the TD

videos.description: Nothing's going well for Mizzou as Malcom Dotson recovers the muffed punt for Purdue.
videos.headline: Boilermakers recover muffed punt

videos.description: Elijah Sindelar's first pass of the game is a 54-yard strike to Cole Herdman.
videos.headline: Sindelar to Herdman for 54-yard gain

videos.description: Elijah Sindelar connects with Jackson Winthrop to widen Purdue's lead in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Sindelar finds Anthrop for score

videos.description: Purdue head coach Jeff Brohm gives some insight on his quarter back situation for the second half.
videos.headline: Brohm gives his thoughts on Purdue's big first half

videos.description: Markus Bailey intercepts Drew Lock as Purdue continues to dominate.
videos.headline: Bailey picks off Lock and returns it for 22 yards

videos.description: David Blough finds Richie Worship for six as Purdue continues to roll.
videos.headline: Blough connects with Worship for the 1-yard TD

videos.description: Kamal Hardy rips the ball out of J'Mon Moore's hands  for another turnover for the Tigers.
videos.headline: Hardy steals ball from Mizzou WR for interception
